    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>White crystalline powder used in electric batteries, in printing, as a soldering flux, and in making other compounds.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
